{"tid":918172,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解你好似唔肯承認段關係","createTime":"2018-11-27T04:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T05:26:45.000Z","uid":176899,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"efb7742785a782e16d81b3316be24337abfe802e","tid":918172,"uid":176899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"男朋友成日都好似好怕俾佢D朋友知佢有女朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次試過佢落堂我搵佢食飯<br />\n好自然一見到就拖住<br />\n但佢同我講 可唔可以唔好拖住我<br />\n佢有解釋話係唔想佢D同學講佢<br />\nOk fine 我都明白<br />\n但個心銀銀住<br />\n<br />\n又會發現佢單獨約女仔食飯<br />\n然而我係事後先知<br />\n有表達過唔中意<br />\n但又好似無咩改善過<br />\n同埋佢好多朋友都係女仔<br />\n所以都好似好難避免？<br />\n唉屌 我都唔撚知<br />\n<br />\n如果要坐低講<br />\n又怕佢覺得我唔信佢咁<br />\n<br />\n究竟應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd91948c491ff34498b6b77ffaad4f0411222a0","tid":918172,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"肥豬員係咁"},{"pid":"b50b243f14ce4ac787863e25102b0ea0b9faf558","tid":918172,"uid":46408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"你太醜樣<br />\n唔見得人<br />\n騎牛搵馬既野 大家心照咪算"},{"pid":"9fa351ab3cd5e2b58813c5839f1f68c700f064b4","tid":918172,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"咁賤既"},{"pid":"d061aed5fe9512c3a378792231b747472cca0c15","tid":918172,"uid":217940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"騎牛揾馬？切得<br />\n好明顯唔認你，約女食飯算點"},{"pid":"79fc6c223c9e7dc2582ae3a80e58989277af6406","tid":918172,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"當你人肉飛機杯咋<br />\n柒下柒下咁"},{"pid":"9c0ea13ac5faa2f5cdadfa41ae9640df31669c62","tid":918172,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"你只係肉便器，ok?"},{"pid":"9cfc99f76b3bd84fb2a250d47f98521e05ab98d7","tid":918172,"uid":